{
  "stem": "27150.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said that Romak didn't play fair with him, because I promised him-- he-- he didn't want to-- he wanted a job, and I couldn't afford to give him a job.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I said, look, you will be my English-speaking man, and I'll give you 10%.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he made a lot of money, and I'm not going to make the mistake once again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at this day, I saw that I am going back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you see, that means he, when Romak was making 10% out of his earning, he was making 90%.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if it is, for Romak, too much money, what can I expect?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you see, they were manufacturing plastic, and Romak was 16% in the business, and Henry had 60%, and there were other partners.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Romak proposed that he would give me 3% out of his share.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Henry gives me 7%, and he said, I don't commit the mistake again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you see, my daughter has a father-in-law, and I have to support him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if I take [INAUDIBLE] into the business, so I'll have trouble with my daughter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, look, that's the same thing you had the trouble with your wife, because I didn't come to work to you in Warsaw as-- as, you see, as a protege.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I brought you the agency of cutting, and I wasn't paid enough either.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she was jealous, because her brother was a messenger boy, and you were an executive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And now, his daughter was jealous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the meantime, you see, Henry divorced his wife, who later died of cancer, and he was sort of living with a French woman.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
